headline: SCIO Launches SCIO Mini 2 Corn - Next-Generation Lab-Grade Moisture Analysis for Corn
summary: Over a thousand scans. Zero shelling. Instant results. That's the promise of the newly launched SCIO Mini 2, a device that helps US corn growers and seed producers measure moisture in the field, which builds on the success of SCIO Mini 1. The new device has already been adopted by agriculture leaders such as Corteva and Syngenta.
